{
    "name": "Fossegrim",
    "type": "monster",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Pale and possessing unnatural beauty, fossegrims are wicked fey who haunt idyllic waterfalls, where they lure the unsuspecting near with song and the promise of treasure, only to drown them. Well built and elf like in appearance, fossegrims are gifted musicians, and their lairs often echo with the sound of bewitching music. They are never without their enchanting instruments."
        }
    ],
